===Tawja===
Itahl Manu Dayak s '''Udil''', yaru dis sin ifrxan lli mmu isti s wassaɣ  '''Mawli''' (ou Maoli) d '''Madani'''.
==Awrri s Nijir==
Lliɣ d yurri s Nijir, rad ixdm zund agyyad (amsmun n imallayn) n tzruft, dar yat lajuns tafransist n immuddutn. Ur ikki yat, siɣ iskr tin igas s wassaɣ {{Tafransist| Agence de tourisme Temet Voyages}}. Mayyad rad issattuy tamallayt ɣ tansruft d kullu tisggiwin n uflla n Nijir. Yiws ɣ twwuriwin n ummussu n tazla Bariz-Dakar, ig yan umddakl lli bahra imḥadan d 
'''Thierry Sabine''' li iskrn mnnaw lafalm zund "Un thé au Sahara" n '''Bernardo Bertolucci'''.
